âœ… Choose SQL (Relational Databases) when:

Use MySQL / PostgreSQL / Oracle if:

Data is highly structured

Schema does not change frequently

You need ACID transactions

You have complex joins & relationships

Data consistency is very critical

ðŸ“Œ Examples:

