âœ… Choose NoSQL (MongoDB, etc.) when:

Use MongoDB / Redis / Cassandra if:

Data is semi-structured or unstructured

Schema changes frequently

Application needs high scalability

Read/write performance is important

Data can be denormalized

ðŸ“Œ Examples:

Social media apps

